SxsltInitializationFunction
                     Set an R function to be called each time
                     the R extension module in XSLT is
                     initialized
Sxsltproc            R function mimicing shell command xsltproc
XMLXPathParserContext-class
                     Class representing the internal data
                     structure for an XSL transformation
XPathNodeSet         Methods for an XPathNodeSet reference
XSLParseEval         Evaluate an S expression from an XSL
                     string
XSLStyleSheet-class
                     Class "XSLStyleSheet" reference to a
                     parsed, internal XSL style sheet
XSLTTransformContext-class
                     Class "XSLTTransformContext"
XSLTemplateDescription-class
                     Description of an XSL template
[.XMLAttributes      Access attributes of XML Node
[.XMLChildren        Get sub-nodes of an XML node
addXSLTFunctions     Queue R functions to registered as XSL
                     functions.
closureGenerator     Programmatically create functions with a
                     shared environment
getTemplate          Find the template to process a node
getXSLParams         Extract the top-level XSL parameters and
                     default values in an XSL stylesheet
getXSLVariables      Get the value of one or more
                     top-level/global XSL parameters
libxsltVersion       Query the version of the libxslt library
                     in use.
processXSLXInclude   Replace the XInclude with the contents to
                     which it refers
readXSL              Read an XSL document as an XML document,
                     substituting import and include nodes with
                     the contents of the referenced documents.
registerXSLFunction
                     Define an XSL extension function
registerXSLTExtension
                     Register a new XSLT extension namespace
saveXML.XMLInternalXSLTDocument
                     Serializes XSLT-processed document to a
                     file or string
toc.XSL              Get a table of contents of templates in an
                     XSL document (and imports)
xslError             R-level functions for signalling errors,
                     warnings and terminating the XSL
                     processing
xslGlobalParameterNames
                     Get the names of the top-level/global XSL
                     parameters
xslImportStyleSheets
                     Import style sheets into an existing XSL
                     style sheet
xsltApplyStyleSheet
                     Process XML document with XSLT stylesheet
xsltCallTemplate     Allow R to invoke an XSL template
xsltGetCurrentTemplate
                     Query the active node or template
xsltGetStyleSheet    Obtain a reference to the XML internal
                     document object for the style sheet or the
                     input XML document.
xsltGetXMLSourceNode
                     Get the active nodes in the XSL process
xsltInsert           Tools for adding nodes to the the
                     target/output document in an XSL
                     transformation.
xsltParseStyleSheet
                     Read XSLT stylesheet into memory
xsltProcessNode      Process a single XML node within the
                     context of an XSL stylesheet and
                     transformation
